
			
									<h5>Release Date: 14 July 2020</h5>
				
									Neo4j 4.1.1 is a maintenance release with many important improvements and fixes.
<h3>Highlights</h3>

<ul>
   <li>Fixes issue where created indexes would stop being resampled after restart</li>
   <li>Fix a bug where deleting a relationship would not remove its entry from any relevant full-text index on relationships such relationships.</li>
   <li>Fix a bug where queries with Aggregations and RETURN * could hang forever during planning.</li>
   <li>Fix so browser doesnâ€™t execute meta query on system db</li>
   <li>Fix displaying large integers in new table correctly</li>

</ul>

